net.sourceforge.js3tream
Class Operation

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.js3tream.Operation
Direct Known Subclasses:
DeleteOperation, ListOperation, StdinOperation, StdoutOperation
public abstract class Operation
extends java.lang.Object

This interface represents all operations. An operation class is created and then started.
